PrecisAmendments to the GOVERNMENT AIRPORT CONCESSION OPERATIONS REGULATIONS which will require anyone who carries on any business or commercial undertaking at an airport to have a permit to do so or to have entered into a lease, licence agreement or contract with the Minister of Transport.
